  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">On-line Education for Lay Counselors</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim is to increase capacity in the community by increasing knowledge and skills and changing attitudes of workers in social reconstruction and regeneration, facilitating individuals and groups to develop new positive life perspectives and create conditions for peace. It includes the ability to cope with psychological traumatization, which is a central problem in creating conditions for peace. It includes communication, civil society, nonviolent conflict transformation, and human rights.</narrative>
  </description>
